---
import profile from "../assets/profile.jpg";
---

<section
  class="aboutme w-3/4 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center"
>
  <h2 class="section-header text-6xl relative left-[200px] top-[25px]">
    ABOUT ME
  </h2>

  <div class="content flex flex-row w-full h-[400px] max-h-[400px]">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center m-5">
      <span class="side-text text-lg">DEVELOPER</span>
    </div>

    <div
      class="picture relative bottom-[30px] max-w-[300px] max-h-[200px] shrink-0"
    >
      <img src={profile.src} alt="Johan's picture" />
    </div>

    <div class="info flex flex-col gap-5 justify-center m-5 p-5">
      <div class="header-info text-lg text-accent">
        <h3>22 YEARS / DR / JUNIOR</h3>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-justify max-w-md">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras eu velit
        lacinia, egestas ex ac, vulputate orci. Sed dictum nulla vel feugiat
        feugiat. Vivamus a orci et nisl pharetra sodales et ac ipsum. Nullam
        porta, ante at euismod placerat, tortor orci dapibus nisl, non fermentum
        ante nisl at nisi. Donec pulvinar, nunc id accumsan dictum, nisl libero
        tristique sem, et ornare felis ex quis diam.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-row space-x-7">
        <a href="#" class="main-link hvr-bounce-to-right w-44 h-10 text-xl"
          >CV</a
        >
        <a
          href="#"
          class="secondary-link hvr-bounce-to-right2 w-44 h-10 text-xl"
          >CONTACT</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .content {
    background: #101112;
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 100px 0px #000;
  }

  .section-header {
    font-family: Cera CY Bold;
  }

  .side-text {
    font-family: Cera CY Bold;
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    text-orientation: upright;
  }

  p {
    font-family: Cera CY Regular;
  }

  .picture img {
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 50px 0px #000;
  }
</style>
